                                        <div class="collapse" id="FAQcollapse629" data-parent="#faqListAccordion">
                                            <div class="collapse-wrapper">
                                                Tetenter is a facilitator of real investments, we do not offer the management of assets. All investment contracts are signed between the borrower and the investor, Tetenter simply facilitates this transaction. All client funds are separated from Tetenter’s operational funds. Should Tetenter suffer financial difficulties or go bankrupt, client funds are safe and can still be accessed. In such an unlikely event, a contractual entity will be appointed to take over the role of Tetenter to serve all the investments.                                            </div>
